#ROOM
Vnum     20560
Name     &rThe Lower Spire Landing&d~
Sector   city~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The high, smoke-choked air of Blackrock Mountain becomes 
oppressive as you step into the lower military hub of the 
Spire. Massive stone stairs wind upward, while high balconies 
overlook the deep pits of the mountain. The sound of 
distant chanting and the clash of steel is constant.
~
#EXIT
Direction out~
ToRoom    36561
Desc      Return to the Hall of the Mountain.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    20561
Desc      The main thoroughfare.~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     20561
Name     &rThe Thoroughfare of War&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A wide hallway built to accommodate the passage of ogre 
armies. The walls are decorated with the tattered banners 
 of the Spirestone and Smolderthorn clans. Spirestone 
ogres patrol the area with heavy clubs.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    20560
Desc      The landing.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    20562
Desc      The Spirestone Commons.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 20500 10 20561
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     20562
Name     &rThe Spirestone Commons - South&d~
Sector   city~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The start of the ogre residential area. Large, messy 
caverns branch off the main path, each filled with 
crude bedding and the remains of many meals.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    20561
Desc      The thoroughfare.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    20563
Desc      The Spirestone Commons Central.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    20590
Desc      Toward the Smolderthorn Quarter.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 20500 10 20562
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     20563
Name     &rThe Spirestone Commons - Central&d~
Sector   city~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The heart of the ogre territory. A massive stone pillar 
in the center is carved with the history of the Spirestone 
clan. Highlord Omokk's throne is visible to the north.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    20562
Desc      The southern commons.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    20564
Desc      The Highlord's Seat.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 20512 5 20563
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     20564
Name     &rThe Throne of Highlord Omokk&d~
Sector   city~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The highest point of the ogre quarters. Highlord Omokk sits 
upon a throne of mismatched skulls and iron, surveying 
his people. To the north, a high bridge leads toward 
the Bloodaxe military district.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    20563
Desc      The central commons.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    20565
Desc      The bridge to the Spire.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 20504 1 20564
  Reset G 1 20531 1
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     20565
Name     &rThe Bridge of the Spire&d~
Sector   city~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A long, narrow stone bridge crossing a massive vertical 
shaft. From here, you can see the Molten Core far below 
and the peaks of the Upper Spire high above. Obsidian 
gargoyles watch from the high rafters.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    20564
Desc      Omokk's throne.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    20566
Desc      The Bloodaxe Garrison.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 20529 5 20565
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     20566
Name     &rThe Bloodaxe Garrison - Entrance&d~
Sector   city~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A heavily fortified stone chamber housing the primary 
guard contingent for the lower Spire. The walls are 
lined with sharp iron halberds and heavy shields.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    20565
Desc      The bridge.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    20567
Desc      The Bloodaxe Courtyard.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 20502 10 20566
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     20567
Name     &rThe Bloodaxe Courtyard&d~
Sector   city~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The center of the military district. Orc soldiers work 
at various crafting stations, and a large bonfire burns 
in the center. Quartermaster Zigris oversees the stores 
from a high platform.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    20566
Desc      The garrison entrance.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    20568
Desc      Toward the Halycon Lair.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    20580
Desc      Toward the Overlord's Balcony.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 20511 1 20567
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     20568
Name     &rThe Hall of the Pack&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The air here is warm and carries the unmistakable scent 
of wet fur. The walls are covered in matted hair and 
gnawed bones.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    20567
Desc      The courtyard.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    20569
Desc      Halycon's Lair.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 20527 10 20568
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     20569
Name     &rThe Lair of Halycon&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A large, dry cavern filled with dozens of white wolf pups. 
The massive winter-wolf Halycon stands in the center, 
her eyes glowing with protective rage.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    20568
Desc      The pack hall.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    20570
Desc      Toward the Slave Pens.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 20509 1 20569
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     20570
Name     &rThe Slave Pens - Entrance&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     Cramped, dirty tunnels where the Dark Horde keeps its 
captives. Gizrul the Slavener can be heard shouting 
orders from the room ahead.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    20569
Desc      Halycon's lair.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    20571
Desc      The Slavener's Seat.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 20510 5 20570
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     20571
Name     &rThe Seat of Gizrul the Slavener&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A high stone ledge overlooking the labor pits. Gizrul 
stands here with a heavy whip, watching the slaves 
work in the heat below.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    20570
Desc      The pens entrance.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 20510 1 20571
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     20580
Name     &rOverlord Wyrmthalak's Balcony&d~
Sector   city~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A grand stone balcony at the highest point of the lower 
Spire. Overlord Wyrmthalak stands here, his wings 
shading the entire floor. He overlooks his domain 
with the cold patience of a dragon.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    20567
Desc      The Bloodaxe courtyard.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
