  Reset G 1 20537 1
  Reset G 1 20548 1
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     20590
Name     &rSmolderthorn Quarter - West&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The architecture here becomes more ornate and troll-like. 
The walls are decorated with colorful feathers and 
stone idols. Troll shadow-hunters move silently 
through the shadows.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    20562
Desc      The Spirestone commons.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    20591
Desc      The Smolderthorn Central.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 20501 10 20590
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     20591
Name     &rThe Smolderthorn Commons - Central&d~
Sector   city~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The heart of the troll district. A large pool of dark 
voodoo-infused water sits in the center of the square. 
War Master Voone's command post is visible to the north.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    20590
Desc      The west quarter.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    20592
