Reset M 0 20513 5 20591
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     20592
Name     &rWar Master Voone's Command Post&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A high room filled with tactical maps and trophies 
taken from the Alliance and Horde. War Master Voone 
stands before a large sand-table, planning the next 
Smolderthorn raid.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    20591
Desc      The central commons.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 20505 1 20592
  Reset G 1 20532 1
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     20593
Name     &rThe Seer's Alcove&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A small, quiet room behind the command post. Smolderthorn 
