with the spirits.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    20592
Desc      The command post.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 20526 5 20593
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     20594
Name     &rTazz'Alaq Tunnels - Entrance&d~
Sector   underground~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The well-maintained stone of the troll quarter gives way to 
